experience.title: Web Developer
description: Highly skilled Frontend and WordPress Developer with a proven track record of delivering over 100+ successful projects. Expertise in HTML, CSS, JavaScript , React , Tailwind ,Bootstrape, PHP and WordPress customization, with a strong focus on creating responsive, user-friendly websites. Adept at collaborating with cross-functional teams to deliver high-quality digital solutions that meet client needs and exceed expectations.
Strong background in frontend development with React.js, gained through an internship at CodexCue.
Proficient in CSS animations, JavaScript, and responsive design.
Developed custom web applications with a focus on performance optimization.
Skilled in using modern frontend frameworks and delivering high-quality results.
Experienced in WordPress and Shopify, working on international live projects and building client websites.
Skilled in theme development, plugin integration, and customization.
Created custom e-commerce solutions and visually appealing, optimized websites.
Strong knowledge of web development tools, delivering high-quality results.
